message:
feat: config.yaml support for v23-v25 engines

Previously v23 PathPolicy, v24 Counterfactual, v25 PlanCompiler/
Capability/Deviation were hardcoded with defaults in main.go.
Config changes via API were lost on restart.

Now all 5 engines read from config.yaml:
- path_policy: { enabled }
- counterfactual: { enabled, mode, max_per_hour, risk_threshold, ... }
- plan_compiler: { enabled, match_threshold, max_active_plans,
    strict_mode, violation_action }
- capability: { enabled, default_policy }
